ink.description: This proxy token (the name) ensures that the system token (the value) maps correctly to the theme setting in Figma. If the token name and the setting variable were exactly the same this wouldn't be needed.

base-family.description: Family tokens designate the overall color set and do not map to explicit values. Therefore, they are blank.

base-darker.description: Affects follow up question container border

base-ink.description: Affects outline button, text and border color of the input, text and border color of the select, text and border color of the textarea
